INTRODUCTION
This project is a fork of opencc (http://code.google.com/p/opencc/) which developed by BYVoid (https://github.com/BYVoid)

This project consists of the followings:
1. opencc (https://github.com/BYVoid/OpenCC)
2. uchardet (https://github.com/BYVoid/uchardet)
3. opencc-gui (https://github.com/BYVoid/opencc-gui)
4. opencc dictionary and config
5. scripts (build and update dictionary)

REQUIREMENTS
1. MinGW (gcc and g++ are required, tested with gcc-4.5.2) and msys 1.0
2. cmake (2.6 or above)
3. Qt (tested with 4.7.3)

INSTALLATION
1. run ./mingw_build.sh in msys shell (ensure cmake and qmake are in the path)
2. the binary will be build in folder 'build'
3. run opencc-gui.ext in folder 'build'
